property.caption: API Key
property.description: API Key used to open a connection to Pusher.

property.caption: API Key Attribute
property.description: (optional) Specify an API Key using an attribute of the context object.

property.caption: cluster
property.description: Cluster in which the app is located.

property.caption: Channel microflow
property.description: Microflow to run when a message is received on this channel. The channel name will be the Mendix object ID of the context object.
